In [4]:
X = []
Y = []
for shoe_folder in os.scandir(filepath): # iterate through subfolders
    shoe_type = os.path.basename(shoe_folder) # Save folder name string for use as shoe label
    pbar = tqdm(os.scandir(shoe_folder.path), total=1000) # Use tqdm iter to display progress of reading in images
    
    for file in pbar: # iterate through files
        pbar.set_description(f"Processing {shoe_type} Images")
        img = cv2.imread(file.path)
        img = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB) # transform defualt read in of cv2 BGR to RGB
        img_array = np.asarray(img)
        
        if img_array.shape != (102,136,3): # Do conditional resizing to save computing power
            img_array = resize(img_array, [n_H,n_W], anti_aliasing=True) # resize to ensure all images are 136 x 102
            
        X.append(img_array)
        Y.append(shoe_type)

# 데이터 분할
num_dev = int(len(X) * dev_size) 
num_test = int(len(X) * test_size)

#데이터 전처리 -> 0~1값으로 변경(RGB)

X_arr = np.asarray(X) / 255
#열 백터 형태로 변환
Y_arr = np.asarray(Y).reshape(-1,1)

del X, Y

ohe = OneHotEncoder(categories='auto', sparse=False)
Y_ohe = ohe.fit_transform(Y_arr)

X_train = X_arr[:-(num_test + num_dev)]
X_dev = X_arr[-(num_test + num_dev):-num_test]
X_test = X_arr[-num_test:]

Y_train = Y_ohe[:-(num_test + num_dev)]
Y_dev = Y_ohe[-(num_test + num_dev):-num_test]
Y_test = Y_ohe[-num_test:]

del X_arr, Y_arr, Y_ohe

print("Training X:", X_train.shape)
print("Training Y:", Y_train.shape)
print("Development X:", X_dev.shape)
print("Development Y:", Y_dev.shape)
print("Test X:", X_test.shape)
print("Test Y:", Y_test.shape)

# 신경망 모델 생성
#모델을 생성하는 코드
model = tf.keras.Sequential(name = 'FirstModel')
model = tf.keras.Sequential(name='CNN')
#-------------------------------------------------------------------------
model.add(layers.Conv2D(32, (5, 5), activation='relu', padding="SAME", input_shape=(n_H, n_W, 3), kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.01), name="c1"))
model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2), padding="SAME", name="m1"))
model.add(layers.Conv2D(64, (5, 5), activation='relu', padding="SAME", kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.01), name="c2"))
model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2), padding="SAME", name="m2"))
model.add(layers.Conv2D(128, (5, 5), activation='relu', padding="SAME", kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.01), name="c3"))
model.add(layers.MaxPooling2D((2, 2), padding="SAME", name="m3"))
model.add(layers.Flatten(name="flat"))
model.add(layers.Dense(256, activation='relu', kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.01), name="d1"))
model.add(layers.Dropout(0.2, name="dd1"))
model.add(layers.Dense(256, activation='relu', kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.01), name="d2"))
model.add(layers.Dropout(0.2, name="dd2"))
model.add(layers.Dense(256, activation='relu', kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l2(0.01), name="d3"))
model.add(layers.Dropout(0.2, name="dd3"))
model.add(layers.Dense( 3, activation='softmax', kernel_initializer='glorot_uniform', name="out"))

# 생성될 신경망 모델 구조 출력
model.summary()

optimizer = tf.keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=0.001)

# 모델 생성
model.compile(
              optimizer=optimizer,
              loss='categorical_crossentropy', #원 핫 인코딩을 사용 -> 비용함수 계산을 크로스 엔트로피로 한다.
              metrics=['accuracy']) # 모델의 평가지표로 정확도를 사용
# 최적화 알고리즘(optimizer) <- 퍼셉트론이기에 학습을 할 은닉층이 없어 생략.

# 모델 학습
history = model.fit(X_train, Y_train, validation_data=(X_dev, Y_dev), epochs=epochs)
